1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,270
[I Don't Want To Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:44,320
One, two, three, four.

4
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:47,150
Up. Five, six, seven, eight.

5
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:49,789
Two, two, three, four.

6
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:52,270
Five, six, seven, eight.

7
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,910
Three, two, three, four.

8
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,310
Mum, I don't want to learn.

9
00:01:57,390 --> 00:01:59,870
Four, two, three, four.

10
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:02,110
Five, six, seven, eight.

11
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,300
Li Jin Bu.

12
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,570
You don't want to learn painting,

13
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:06,900
singing,

14
00:02:06,990 --> 00:02:08,479
and not even dancing.

15
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:09,960
What do you want to learn?

16
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:12,940
My naughty little girl,
what do you want to learn?

17
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,590
Mum, are you ready?

18
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,990
I'm going to attack.

19
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:18,050
Li Jin Bu.

20
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,140
It's raining.

21
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:20,890
Shall we go home?

22
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,160
No, I want to play
regardless of the weather.

23
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,590
Okay,
you stay here and play by yourself.

24
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:25,740
I'm leaving.

25
00:02:25,829 --> 00:02:26,950
I'm going home.

26
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,829
How can I play basketball by myself?

27
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,520
I need an opponent.

28
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,610
Shoot!

29
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,670
Am I the opponent?

30
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,450
Are you going to play against me?

31
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,510
Come on.
Let's see who can win.

32
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,630
Come on. Ready...

33
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:38,930
Come on...

34
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:43,760
[Episode 6: In the name of basketball]

35
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,700
No, no, no. Wait a minute!

36
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,740
Why can't you speak politely?

37
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:53,900
Haven't we already reconciled?

38
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,860
Put your coat on.

39
00:03:00,950 --> 00:03:01,630
Go.

40
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,440
What?

41
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:03,560
Go.

42
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,940
We're not in school.

43
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,580
We are not afraid of these little brats!

44
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,430
I'm telling you to go!

45
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,980
Can't you hear me?

46
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,120
Go if you dare. Go on.

47
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,910
-He was visibly afraid.
-Go.

48
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,230
Xiao Huo, what are you doing?

49
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,660
Come here quickly.

50
00:03:50,010 --> 00:03:51,110
Are you still angry?

51
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,890
You're a big boy now.

52
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,020
But you still fight every day.

53
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,660
Are you going to live by fighting?

54
00:04:00,070 --> 00:04:01,700
That's because they smashed you.

55
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,440
Not you, the snowman.

56
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:04,350
It's okay.

57
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:06,540
Let's build a better snowman
for our buddy.

58
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,230
Come on, let's go.

59
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:10,620
I'll treat you to a barbecue.

60
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,010
Do you want to go?

61
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,079
I want to eat beef back strap.

62
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:23,420
One, two, three!

63
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,000
Wait!

64
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:26,130
Guys,

65
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:28,570
Li Jin Bu just came back from the south.

66
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,710
Shouldn't we give her

67
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,020
a northeastern welcome ceremony?

68
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:33,180
How's that?

69
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:35,310
What are you doing?

70
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,370
Run!

71
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,420
What?

72
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,130
Good!

73
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:42,460
Three, two, one!

74
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,080
Who was it?

75
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,370
Don't run!

76
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:02,480
♫ The right person is the rule ♫

77
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,590
♫ Only wish to go with you ♫

78
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:08,340
♫ Walking non-stop ♫

79
00:05:08,340 --> 00:05:11,630
♫ You are like the spring breeze,
so tender ♫

80
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:13,770
♫ Let me hold your hand ♫

81
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:16,380
♫ My pulse beats wildly ♫

82
00:05:16,970 --> 00:05:21,800
♫ Luckily, I am where you are ♫

83
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,520
♫ I don't want to be just a friend ♫

84
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:27,690
♫ I want to rely on you,
the sweet climate ♫

85
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:30,340
♫ No matter how long we are together ♫

86
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:34,230
♫ You still make me feel excited ♫

87
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:37,409
♫ I want to tell you my dream last night ♫

88
00:05:37,409 --> 00:05:40,690
♫ I hope to dream
all my future dreams with you ♫

89
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,650
Where is Chen Jun He?

90
00:05:42,730 --> 00:05:44,340
Un...Uncle, you are here.

91
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,360
You stop!

92
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:55,770
Didn't you say

93
00:05:55,890 --> 00:05:57,140
it was a big dog?

94
00:05:57,770 --> 00:06:00,260
Maybe it's the big dog's baby.

95
00:06:02,590 --> 00:06:03,620
All right.

96
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:06,050
[In my short 17-year life,]

97
00:06:06,250 --> 00:06:09,040
[this has to be the best
vacation I've ever had.]

98
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,430
[However,]

99
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:13,280
[this is merely
Li Qing Tong's daily life.]

100
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:16,690
[I suddenly began to
envy her for the first time.]

101
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,010
[At least]

102
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,870
[until the age of 17,]

103
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:23,170
[she had the freedom and
happiness I didn't have.]

104
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,920
[For the first time,]

105
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:27,010
[I have so many friends.]

106
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,150
[It is also the first time]

107
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,970
[I realize that being needed and loved]

108
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:34,020
[feels so wonderful.]

109
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:43,520
[Prosperity]

110
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,620
Hua, please help me
to see if it is crooked.

111
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,970
Go up a little bit.

112
00:06:47,610 --> 00:06:48,950
A little bit to the left.

113
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,920
Almost.

114
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,180
The dumplings are almost cooked.

115
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,880
You save two for me.

116
00:07:00,990 --> 00:07:02,650
Will I eat all the dumplings?

117
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,310
Honey, keep an eye on the pot for me.

118
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,270
I'll take this out first.

119
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,240
Okay.

120
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,830
Here comes the dumplings.

121
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,510
Kids, get seated.

122
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,980
Let's eat.

123
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,670
The Spring Festival Gala has begun.

124
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:18,080
Li, here.

125
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,470
It's New Year's Day.

126
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:21,050
Rewarding you a bottle of liquor.

127
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,850
You are kind to me.

128
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:26,030
Mum, this is a wonderful
dinner you've cooked.

129
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,600
It's all meat.

130
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,220
It's a piece of cake.

131
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,710
Who will appear in this
year's Spring Festival Gala?

132
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,190
I heard Xie Xiao Dong will
perform this year.

133
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,670
I've been following him lately.

134
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,950
Who is Xie Xiao Dong?

135
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,930
Don't you know Xie Xiao Dong?

136
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,310
The one who sings health
song with Fan Xiao Xuan.

137
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,150
I know Fan Xiao Xuan,
the rock singer.

138
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,270
Fan Xiao Xuan.

139
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,850
The little witch.

140
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,990
Okay, let's stop talking.

141
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,740
Get ready to eat.

142
00:07:49,150 --> 00:07:50,180
Say something.

143
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,540
It must be a New Year's call.

144
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,360
Hello.

145
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,690
Here.

146
00:07:58,280 --> 00:08:00,020
A big red envelope for each person.

147
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,130
Thanks, auntie.

148
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:02,340
Thanks, Mum.

149
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,020
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

150
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:05,700
You should all study hard next year.

151
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,780
Stop looking.

152
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,070
Hey, where are my New Year wishes?

153
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,600
Study hard next year.

154
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,560
Come on.

155
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,900
Who was that?

156
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:19,140
New Year greetings from factory workers.

157
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,430
-Come.
-Let's get started.

158
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,710
Okay. Let's have a drink.

159
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,030
Let's have a drink.

160
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,790
Here.

161
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:27,650
Happy New Year!

162
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,950
Help yourself.

163
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,740
Li, how do you like the dumplings?

164
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:43,720
[Prosperity]

165
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:47,940
I ate too much this evening

166
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,420
that I can't sleep.

167
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,180
Then you can get up and study.

168
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:54,730
Who studies on New Year's Eve?

169
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:56,180
Fifteen days are up.

170
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,250
Did you forget?

171
00:08:57,990 --> 00:08:59,130
Goodnight.

172
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:01,950
Li Qing Tong.

173
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,090
I'm asleep.

174
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:17,530
Are they asleep?

175
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,580
Who called just now?

176
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,620
Mr Wang.

177
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:33,730
What about?

178
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:40,600
He told me that

179
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,940
I don't have to work after the New Year.

180
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,600
What's the matter?

181
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:50,480
The factory was closed down.

182
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:55,990
How could such a big factory

183
00:09:58,470 --> 00:10:00,290
close down so suddenly?

184
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:18,180
Tong Tong is going to college soon,

185
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:21,200
and now is the time we need money.

186
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,480
Okay.

187
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:25,870
I'll find a way.

188
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:27,430
Don't worry about it.

189
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:31,310
Don't let the kids know about this.

190
00:10:50,570 --> 00:10:53,340
[Electrician]

191
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:56,720
Come, come. Range hood repair.

192
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,470
Come, come. Range hood repair.

193
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,180
Bricklayer...

194
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,180
Bricklayer...

195
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:06,320
[Bricklayer, available all year.
Paid by day]

196
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,910
[Painter]

197
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:13,880
Brother, you know a lot of skills.

198
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:15,390
[Professional handyman]

199
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:16,430
Not bad.

200
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,430
I wonder

201
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,230
how much money you make a day?

202
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,270
30 or 40 yuan.

203
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,700
30 or 40 yuan?

204
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,230
There are times when things are rough?

205
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,230
Sometimes a day goes by without work.

206
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:29,160
-So you stand here?
-Stand here for a day.

207
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:31,160
Just asking.

208
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,310
Okay. Thanks, brother.

209
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,080
Bye.

210
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:34,960
Call me if you need.

211
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,180
Okay, fine.

212
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:37,940
Come on, brother.

213
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:39,760
Do you need
to repair the range hood?

214
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,510
I don't need it.

215
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:42,730
It's okay, 30 yuan a day.

216
00:11:42,730 --> 00:11:47,360
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

217
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,790
In view of last term,

218
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,770
our overall situation was not so good.

219
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,910
The school decided that

220
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,830
the new semester must
have a new atmosphere.

221
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:56,320
I want to improve the overall
performance of Class 3.

222
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:57,310
I announce that

223
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,690
starting from this semester,

224
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,940
we will have a quiz once a month.

225
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:03,780
Don't sigh and pout.

226
00:12:03,950 --> 00:12:05,410
I haven't announced the big agenda.

227
00:12:07,250 --> 00:12:08,430
I announce that

228
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:09,840
starting from this semester,

229
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:12,090
we will set up one-to-one
study groups.

230
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:13,610
The school has approved it.

231
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,470
We will implement it

232
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,350
as an extracurricular
project this semester.

233
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,570
In principle,

234
00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:19,480
a student who studies well

235
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:21,600
will lead a student who
is not good at learning.

236
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,230
The two form a team

237
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,430
and use self-study
and extracurricular time

238
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,830
for mutual assistance in learning.

239
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,350
If necessary,

240
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,460
you can apply for a seat exchange.

241
00:12:30,570 --> 00:12:32,470
You can choose
your partner by yourself.

242
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,070
In these few months,

243
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,870
we will strive to enter Year 3

244
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,410
with a better overall result.

245
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,710
At the end of the term,
I will make a ranking

246
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,710
according to the total
score of the two people.

247
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:41,910
The top ten will be rewarded,

248
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,030
and the last ten will be punished.

249
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,060
Do you understand?

250
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,090
Monitor,

251
00:12:45,290 --> 00:12:46,370
after class,

252
00:12:46,450 --> 00:12:48,350
organize several people to
write this form on the blackboard.

253
00:12:48,430 --> 00:12:50,350
Write down the name
of the person you team up with

254
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,340
for clear supervision at any time.

255
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:53,930
Mr Wu,

256
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,670
what if no one wants to be with me?

257
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,230
Think about it yourself.

258
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,980
You are a failure. Are you ashamed?

259
00:12:59,430 --> 00:13:00,310
I'm not talking about myself.

260
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,700
Many classmates choose me.

261
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,250
You can discuss it
by yourself after class.

262
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:04,150
If you can't choose,

263
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,190
I'll assign it for you directly.

264
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:07,070
Let's start.

265
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,100
Stand up.

266
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:16,640
I think this must be the
opportunity created by God for me.

267
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:19,260
Are you still thinking about it?

268
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,140
Sure.

269
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,460
I must make Wu Zhi Xun
and Li Qing Tong a team.

270
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,890
All the best then.

271
00:13:28,690 --> 00:13:29,560
Hua,

272
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:31,590
I am suddenly a little worried.

273
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,740
We are definitely a team.

274
00:13:33,830 --> 00:13:35,350
What about Fan Shui Shui?

275
00:13:36,090 --> 00:13:37,380
You think too much.

276
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:38,680
Who said I will be on your team?

277
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,070
You're not my business.

278
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:46,810
I guess you and I are a team.

279
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,430
Us?

280
00:13:49,530 --> 00:13:51,580
Can you help me or can I help you?

281
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:54,420
Can our total score
be higher than that of one person?

282
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:56,200
What's the point?

283
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,550
Li Qing Tong, you barely
got 20 points.

284
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:00,490
How could you criticize me?

285
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:02,960
That's why I need to find someone useful.

286
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,180
Li Qing Tong.

287
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,290
Who are you saying is useless?

288
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:13,960
Do you want it?

289
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,080
No.

290
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:20,760
What do you like to eat?

291
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:22,660
I should have said

292
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,370
I don't want anything to do with you.

293
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,710
What kind of sports do you like?

294
00:14:30,830 --> 00:14:32,490
Such as playing basketball?

295
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,660
-Or...
-Wu Zhi Xun.

296
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:40,210
Are you free now?

297
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:43,260
I want to talk to you
about the support group.

298
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:44,450
I'm sorry.

299
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:46,520
I won't team up with anyone.

300
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,180
Brother, throw the ball over.

301
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,020
Come on, I'll serve.

302
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:37,420
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

303
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:08,380
Don't cheat.

304
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,710
I think someone is ready to do it.

305
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,300
Don't think I can't see it.

306
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:20,970
Xiao.

307
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,550
Xiao.

308
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:34,060
Hey. What are you doing, sir?

309
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,530
Don't you know?

310
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,910
The hat will be yours from now on.

311
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,670
Wear it for the test.

312
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,230
I can't see anything.

313
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:41,300
What do you want to see during the test?

314
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:58,560
I don't have it.

315
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:07,300
Xiao.

316
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,099
Xiao.

317
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,619
Where is the answer?

318
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,460
Hurry up.

319
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:43,360
Tell me.

320
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:46,420
Who wrote the answer
and who is it for?

321
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:48,470
No one.

322
00:18:48,550 --> 00:18:49,820
I wrote it myself.

323
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,150
Your score is so low

324
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,320
and you want to help others?

325
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,940
Who are you fooling?

326
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,860
I really wrote this myself.

327
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:58,040
Okay. You wrote it.

328
00:18:58,120 --> 00:18:59,530
Who are you going to give it to?

329
00:19:01,010 --> 00:19:02,910
You saw it fall on the monitor's desk.

330
00:19:03,190 --> 00:19:04,550
Wang Xiao Min, don't talk nonsense!

331
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,050
Why did you throw it to me?

332
00:19:06,660 --> 00:19:08,080
You're really good, aren't you?

333
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:09,600
You were ranked outside
of 100 in the school,

334
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,640
and you wrote answers for the top three.

335
00:19:10,730 --> 00:19:12,040
Are you trying to raise her grade?

336
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:14,550
We are classmates.

337
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:16,340
I just gave her a hand.

338
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,430
Shut up!

339
00:19:17,540 --> 00:19:18,470
Mr Wu,

340
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:19,720
I know the truth.

341
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:22,680
I saw Wang Xiao Min and Li Qing Tong
exchanging signals.

342
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:24,190
He must have wanted to
pass it on to Li Qing Tong.

343
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:25,550
He threw it to me by mistake.

344
00:19:25,630 --> 00:19:27,700
Lin Xue Wei, what are you talking about?

345
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,380
This is pure slander!

346
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,110
I just kept my head
down to write the paper.

347
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,630
No one signalled at him.

348
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:35,310
Sir, I have something to say.

349
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,110
I saw Lin Xue Wei pass
a note to Bai Ling Er.

350
00:19:37,190 --> 00:19:38,150
Fan Shui Shui, you are
not quite right in the head.

351
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,550
You cheat and blame others.

352
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,670
We don't have any evidence,

353
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:41,550
so let's all blow the whistle.

354
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,470
Sir, I still have something to say.

355
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:43,570
Shut up!

356
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:45,240
Sit down!

357
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:49,610
What's your right to be angry!

358
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:52,200
I ask again for the last time.

359
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,900
Who admits it?

360
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:56,740
If no one admits,
it will be all on Wang Xiao Min.

361
00:19:56,990 --> 00:19:57,950
Do you hear me?

362
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:59,180
Cheating during exams.

363
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:01,200
Covering up the accomplices.

364
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:02,760
Faulting classmates.

365
00:20:02,850 --> 00:20:04,060
Get your parents here or

366
00:20:04,170 --> 00:20:05,230
drop out of the school.

367
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:06,670
Get your parents here tomorrow.

368
00:20:06,770 --> 00:20:07,840
Get out, now!

369
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,590
No. Wait, sir...

370
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,380
Is it that serious?

371
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:16,300
Sir.

372
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:17,610
It was me.

373
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:25,930
Duan Xiao.

374
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:28,530
How did you get involved in this?

375
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:31,170
Why don't you learn from good classmates?

376
00:20:31,610 --> 00:20:32,880
All right.
Who is the other one?

377
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,320
Admit it now.

378
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:35,850
Who!

379
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,940
He... He

380
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,460
wrote to him and he threw it to me.

381
00:20:51,630 --> 00:20:52,510
Alright.

382
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,460
You guys are really ambitious.

383
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:57,910
This cheating attempt has failed.

384
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,420
I will give you a chance.

385
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:00,760
How should we deal with it?

386
00:21:01,490 --> 00:21:02,320
Sir,

387
00:21:02,410 --> 00:21:04,910
we can write a detailed report

388
00:21:05,050 --> 00:21:06,190
to reflect on our mistakes.

389
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:07,360
And then?

390
00:21:08,530 --> 00:21:09,140
That's it.

391
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,220
That's all?

392
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:11,550
Sir,

393
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,160
I have a good suggestion.

394
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,920
The sports day is coming soon.

395
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,390
Get them to run.

396
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,310
Run more laps.

397
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,590
Maybe the good result of the competition

398
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:19,760
can be used as merit

399
00:21:19,840 --> 00:21:21,540
and win glory for the class.

400
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,420
I think it's a good idea.

401
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,580
Do you agree?

402
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:26,570
Let me be clear.

403
00:21:26,670 --> 00:21:27,600
This is all voluntary.

404
00:21:27,710 --> 00:21:29,220
It doesn't matter if you don't agree.

405
00:21:29,290 --> 00:21:30,040
I'll go to Ms Yang

406
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:31,270
and see what we can do about it.

407
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:32,420
No, don't!

408
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:34,410
I agree.

409
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:35,750
I'll run.

410
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:36,710
Yes.

411
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:37,750
It's exercise.

412
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:39,020
It's a good thing.

413
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:41,810
Go ahead, go for a run.

414
00:21:41,900 --> 00:21:42,900
Run now.

415
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:54,740
How many laps?

416
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,760
Ten laps.

417
00:21:57,230 --> 00:21:58,110
What?

418
00:21:58,230 --> 00:22:00,070
Didn't I run ten laps just now?

419
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:01,680
Be contented.

420
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,590
If it's not snowing heavily,

421
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,580
I'll let you run large laps.

422
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:05,710
It should be 13 laps now.

423
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:07,980
Everyone seems to be in a good mood.

424
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:11,960
What are you doing?

425
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,260
Tong.

426
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:31,390
Are you okay?

427
00:22:39,110 --> 00:22:40,370
Hua, listen to me.

428
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:41,850
Let's talk about it at home.

429
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:45,860
Why did you help them cheat?

430
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:47,830
Just this once.

431
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:49,510
They begged me several times

432
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:50,950
before I agreed this time.

433
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,630
It's for your sake.

434
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,710
What do you mean for my sake?

435
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:56,500
Did I ask you to help them cheat?

436
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:58,930
It failed anyway, right?

437
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,870
You guys never listen to me.

438
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:01,810
I don't care anymore.

439
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,150
Come on. Don't be angry.

440
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,210
It won't happen again. I promise.

441
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,470
Hua!

442
00:23:07,190 --> 00:23:09,490
Hua.

443
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,810
Why does it seem like
we're all afraid of Hua?

444
00:23:14,330 --> 00:23:15,550
Why is that?

445
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:18,720
Do you even have to ask why?

446
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:21,050
If you kick Chen Jun He's face

447
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:22,880
and then have a fight with Yang Ai Ling,

448
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,980
the whole school will
be afraid of you too.

449
00:23:28,390 --> 00:23:31,130
I'd have to have
several lives to do that.

450
00:23:33,410 --> 00:23:34,610
I'm exhausted.

451
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,180
What are you doing?

452
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:46,900
Walking.

453
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,370
Did you do that on purpose?

454
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,480
Yes.

455
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:50,840
If you can snitch on me on purpose,

456
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:52,380
why can't I hit you on purpose?

457
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:53,900
Li Qing Tong.

458
00:23:53,990 --> 00:23:55,630
You cheated in the exam.

459
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:57,420
but you dare not admit it.

460
00:24:00,710 --> 00:24:02,740
Do not pretend to be so upright.

461
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,820
It's obviously a personal revenge
taken by a two-faced person.

462
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:07,510
I advise you to study hard.

463
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:09,140
You can't even use the words right.

464
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,780
You're just jealous of us.

465
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:14,260
Am I jealous of you?

466
00:24:14,850 --> 00:24:16,200
Why should I be jealous?

467
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:17,490
Am I jealous of your bad grades?

468
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,000
Jealous that you stir up
trouble everywhere

469
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:21,520
or the fact that you guys
are a bunch of good-for-nothing misfits?

470
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:22,900
Ridiculous.

471
00:24:23,970 --> 00:24:25,020
What do you mean?

472
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:27,100
What are you calling good-for-nothing?

473
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:28,830
Who is the misfit?

474
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,900
You are no different.

475
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,230
Hua.

476
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:59,860
You can be angry with me,

477
00:25:00,300 --> 00:25:02,200
but please

478
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:07,320
don't tell my mother, will you?

479
00:25:07,700 --> 00:25:09,460
If you tell her, I will...

480
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:11,500
I'll die.

481
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,800
Don't worry.

482
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:16,900
I'm not the kind person to tell on others.

483
00:25:17,070 --> 00:25:18,390
I know

484
00:25:18,670 --> 00:25:20,370
you are the most loyal person.

485
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,830
I've figured it out.

486
00:25:22,930 --> 00:25:23,950
I can't save you.

487
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:25,020
I give up.

488
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,580
Then I don't have to go on studying

489
00:25:28,900 --> 00:25:30,300
when I come back from school?

490
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:32,970
That's great.

491
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:36,260
You finally figured it out, Hua.

492
00:25:38,460 --> 00:25:39,430
But,

493
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:41,620
me giving up doesn't mean you should.

494
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:48,590
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

495
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:58,820
Is that your name?

496
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,980
[Li Jin Bu, Duan Xiao]

497
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,080
Believe me,

498
00:26:22,170 --> 00:26:24,320
it is the best choice for us to team up.

499
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,560
Listen to me.

500
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,060
My Chinese and Ma...

501
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:38,230
[Li Jin Bu, Duan Xiao]

502
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,490
The writing was too ugly.

503
00:26:50,880 --> 00:27:00,470
[Li Jin Bu, Duan Xiao]

504
00:27:02,090 --> 00:27:03,750
Mao is a traitor.

505
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:05,700
He's shameless.

506
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:07,270
He pestered Lin Xue Wei to join his team.

507
00:27:07,360 --> 00:27:09,250
Then you have to team
up with Fan Shui Shui.

508
00:27:10,180 --> 00:27:11,360
I'll quit.

509
00:27:11,450 --> 00:27:12,760
Go ahead.

510
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:13,890
Hey.

511
00:27:13,980 --> 00:27:15,850
What kind of friend deserts his brother?

512
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:17,280
So, what can I do for you?

513
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,380
Who do you want to team up with?

514
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:19,630
I'll try my best to help you.

515
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,740
Okay?

516
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,540
Lin Xue Wei.

517
00:27:28,430 --> 00:27:29,930
Lick the bar and I'll help you.

518
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:31,160
Am I sick?

519
00:27:31,250 --> 00:27:32,310
Bye.

520
00:27:32,910 --> 00:27:33,790
Fine.

521
00:27:34,430 --> 00:27:36,060
Will you really help me if I lick it?

522
00:28:14,530 --> 00:28:18,100
[Are you really not going
to team up with anyone?]

523
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:37,590
[Do you like playing basketball?]

524
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:56,410
[Be quiet]

525
00:29:04,970 --> 00:29:06,650
[You are sick]

526
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:13,820
Top student,

527
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,900
finally baffled you?

528
00:29:22,320 --> 00:29:23,990
You are sick!

529
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:26,870
Sir, we are all here.

530
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:27,840
Good.

531
00:29:28,150 --> 00:29:29,160
-Mao Ying Jian.
-I'm here.

532
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,670
When will the name list
of the basketball match

533
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:31,870
of your class be handed in?

534
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,510
Sir, we can not get
enough people in our class.

535
00:29:33,600 --> 00:29:34,790
Can't you find five people in your class?

536
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,580
What's wrong with your class?

537
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:37,910
We can find five.

538
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,260
But we are short of a substitute.

539
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,870
Then, what about the other guys?

540
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,430
Can't they play as a substitute?

541
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:44,830
I tell you that all the other
classes are fighting for places.

542
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:47,500
Sir, they are not tall enough.

543
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,660
Wu Zhi Xun's height is quite appropriate.

544
00:29:50,870 --> 00:29:51,630
Wu Zhi Xun.

545
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:52,830
Can you play basketball?

546
00:29:52,910 --> 00:29:53,900
Sir,

547
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:55,420
you're expecting too much.

548
00:29:55,510 --> 00:29:57,620
He, the top in the grade,
puts his mind on learning.

549
00:29:57,710 --> 00:29:59,150
How does he have time to play basketball?

550
00:29:59,240 --> 00:29:59,910
That's right.

551
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:01,030
It's no use being tall.

552
00:30:01,130 --> 00:30:02,960
Don't make him lose face since
he can't play basketball at all.

553
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:04,500
Who said I can't play?

554
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:08,640
I just don't want to.

555
00:30:09,190 --> 00:30:10,060
All right.

556
00:30:10,360 --> 00:30:11,670
Then find a substitute

557
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,870
and hand in the name list first.

558
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:13,520
Okay.

559
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:15,190
Go back to the team
and lead the warm up.

560
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,160
Yes, sir.

561
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:21,630
Chest extension, ready.

562
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:24,910
One, two, three, four.

563
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:28,060
Five, six, seven, eight.

564
00:30:29,280 --> 00:30:31,260
Wait for your new teacher.

565
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:33,780
What? New teacher?

566
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:36,870
Three, two, three, four.

567
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,570
Five, six, seven, eight.

568
00:30:58,540 --> 00:31:00,000
You like basketball, don't you?

569
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,240
I'll teach you

570
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:07,470
in a month.

571
00:31:09,970 --> 00:31:11,770
I have no interest in playing basketball.

572
00:31:11,990 --> 00:31:14,320
Are you interested in what
other people think of you?

573
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:19,090
I know you love basketball,

574
00:31:19,470 --> 00:31:21,010
but you don't have time to practice

575
00:31:21,230 --> 00:31:23,210
and hate to admit you
don't know how to play.

576
00:31:23,830 --> 00:31:25,400
I'll help you.

577
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,510
I'll teach you

578
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:29,150
how to play basketball in a month.

579
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:31,140
Let you beat them on the match

580
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:32,690
to save your face.

581
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:34,250
What do you think?

582
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,520
Why?

583
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:39,680
What?

584
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:41,650
Why are you helping me?

585
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:44,450
I have a request.

586
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,370
What request?

587
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,420
You team up with Li Qing Tong

588
00:31:50,710 --> 00:31:51,850
to help her study.

589
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:53,460
Li Qing Tong?

590
00:31:54,690 --> 00:31:55,870
Who?

591
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:01,240
Can't you even remember
the name of your classmate?

592
00:32:01,390 --> 00:32:02,470
I only remember the name,

593
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:03,900
not the face.

594
00:32:04,530 --> 00:32:05,820
It doesn't matter who it is.

595
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,580
Just promise me.

596
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,070
I'll think about it.

597
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:11,070
At 8 o'clock this evening,

598
00:32:11,210 --> 00:32:12,720
I'll wait for you at the basketball court

599
00:32:12,810 --> 00:32:14,190
behind the ironworks.

600
00:32:21,910 --> 00:32:23,210
Do your homework first.

601
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:24,400
When you finish,

602
00:32:24,520 --> 00:32:26,580
I'll tell you a great news.

603
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:29,630
Why don't you tell me right now?

604
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:32,620
At least to give me
some motivation to study.

605
00:32:33,210 --> 00:32:34,580
After you finish your homework,

606
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:36,360
I'll take you to meet someone.

607
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:40,040
Who are you meeting at this late hour?

608
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,710
Will he come?

609
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:45,590
I don't know.

610
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:47,020
Let's wait and see.

611
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:53,320
Go in, go in.

612
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,780
Is my braid still in place?

613
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:02,350
I knew for certain that you would come.

614
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:04,420
Come on.

615
00:33:08,530 --> 00:33:10,070
Have you ever played before?

616
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:11,490
Just when I was a kid.

617
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:12,480
What about you?

618
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:15,500
You don't trust me?

619
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:16,940
Watch me.

620
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,830
You will practice this move

621
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,530
for three hours a day

622
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:33,230
and six hours on Saturdays.

623
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:34,700
The exact time depends on you.

624
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:40,990
Don't worry.

625
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:42,940
I know you don't want to
be seen by others.

626
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:44,390
I've checked this place.

627
00:33:44,470 --> 00:33:46,050
No one comes at night.

628
00:33:56,070 --> 00:33:57,530
Why is she here?

629
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:00,900
Come on out.

630
00:34:02,650 --> 00:34:03,880
Don't be mad.

631
00:34:03,970 --> 00:34:05,560
I do need help.

632
00:34:05,670 --> 00:34:06,940
She will take care of things

633
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:08,150
and buy some water.

634
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:09,780
I promise she won't tell.

635
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:11,989
I...I'm with you.

636
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:14,060
I promise I won't say a word.

637
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:16,780
I'll just stand there and not say a word.

638
00:34:19,889 --> 00:34:21,350
Take off your glasses.

639
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:24,110
I...

640
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:25,219
Let me hold it for you.

641
00:34:28,770 --> 00:34:29,650
Come on.

642
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:30,840
Let's start from the basics.

643
00:34:30,949 --> 00:34:32,489
Let's go to the free throw line.

644
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:34,600
First,

645
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:35,780
keep your weight down,

646
00:34:36,250 --> 00:34:37,219
Squat position.

647
00:34:37,989 --> 00:34:39,710
Guard the ball with your left hand.

648
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,159
Pay attention to your opponent.

649
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,469
Pick up the ball,

650
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:43,699
pull back your back foot.

651
00:34:45,570 --> 00:34:46,739
A little wider.

652
00:34:47,239 --> 00:34:48,219
Step up.

653
00:34:48,429 --> 00:34:49,460
Lay up.

654
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:51,280
Do you understand?

655
00:34:51,790 --> 00:34:52,850
You try it again.

656
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:01,590
When shooting,

657
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:03,410
bend your arm 90 degrees.

658
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:04,600
90 degrees.

659
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:07,350
And then use your other hand as support.

660
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,550
When shooting the ball,

661
00:35:09,720 --> 00:35:10,750
press your wrist

662
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:12,490
and throw it out.

663
00:35:13,250 --> 00:35:14,350
Have a try.

664
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,900
90 degrees.

665
00:35:17,270 --> 00:35:18,150
Here.

666
00:35:18,370 --> 00:35:19,250
Right.

667
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,490
Good.

668
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,820
Try throwing it.

669
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,270
Why did you make him
practice just one move?

670
00:35:25,270 --> 00:35:27,070
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

671
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,310
There is no way.

672
00:35:28,390 --> 00:35:29,410
It's impossible for him

673
00:35:29,490 --> 00:35:31,310
to become a master in just one month.

674
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,190
Those boys have been playing
basketball since they were young.

675
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,910
It's easy for them to
see Wu Zhi Xun's level.

676
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:36,560
He can't hide it.

677
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,850
So, what else can we do?

678
00:35:38,220 --> 00:35:39,930
This is the only move he can practice.

679
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,400
Controlling the ball is the foundation

680
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:43,350
[and layup is the
easiest way to get points.]

681
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,830
[He'll practice these two moves
for a month]

682
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,070
[to strengthen his muscle memory.]

683
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,350
[I'm confident that when he plays,]

684
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,380
[he will be as good as anyone else.]

685
00:35:55,910 --> 00:35:56,940
Nice!

686
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:58,160
Missed it.

687
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:01,980
I didn't see it clearly.

688
00:36:02,590 --> 00:36:03,570
Once again.

689
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:09,750
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

690
00:36:12,270 --> 00:36:13,570
Yes, that's right.

691
00:36:38,750 --> 00:36:39,980
Have a rest.

692
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:41,750
You have been playing all night.

693
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:43,510
It's been a long time

694
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,850
and I'm out of practice.

695
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,610
You said you were the best.

696
00:36:46,810 --> 00:36:48,300
That was at my place.

697
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,280
I can hardly breathe in this frigid cold.

698
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,820
How can I play well?

699
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,300
I can't believe you are laughing.

700
00:36:58,830 --> 00:37:00,530
I've never seen that before, too.

701
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:03,640
Go on.

702
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:07,360
Good.

703
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:08,700
Nice!

704
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:15,210
It's too cold. I'm going
to do some exercise.

705
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:16,510
You still have a cold.

706
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:17,410
Can you do it?

707
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:19,580
I never recovered since coming here.

708
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:23,840
Wu Zhi Xun.

709
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,380
Come here and have a rest.

710
00:37:33,270 --> 00:37:34,370
Hua.

711
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:37,500
Are you okay?

712
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:38,190
Don't touch me.

713
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,820
My knee, it hurts.

714
00:37:40,090 --> 00:37:42,440
[Tieyuan Public Hospital]

715
00:37:46,750 --> 00:37:48,890
Doctor, what happened?

716
00:37:49,570 --> 00:37:50,540
Nothing serious.

717
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:51,850
No bones broken.

718
00:37:52,020 --> 00:37:53,360
Go back and have a rest.

719
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,590
Come back next week for a follow-up.

720
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:56,780
That's good.
Thank you, doctor.

721
00:37:56,990 --> 00:37:57,830
Come.

722
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,210
Be careful.

723
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,760
Here, take it.

724
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,700
Thank you.

725
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:11,420
Take good care of Mr Xu.

726
00:38:11,610 --> 00:38:12,610
I'll see him later.

727
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:14,000
-Okay.
-Okay, bye.

728
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:14,970
See you later.

729
00:38:17,370 --> 00:38:20,090
I told you not to get up.
You didn't listen to me.

730
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:21,790
How can you handle this right now?

731
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:42,980
I'll go now.

732
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,580
Have a good rest.

733
00:38:50,090 --> 00:38:51,140
Thank you.

734
00:38:55,790 --> 00:38:56,970
Come over to my house

735
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,700
when you have time.

736
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:11,090
Can you read it?

737
00:39:12,390 --> 00:39:13,830
Why not?

738
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:17,220
I thought of someone.

739
00:39:17,340 --> 00:39:18,180
Mr Xu.

740
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,480
He learns Chinese acupuncture.

741
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,220
I'll call him over.

742
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:22,120
Are you kidding me? Listen.

743
00:39:22,200 --> 00:39:24,110
His wife fell down a few days ago.

744
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,080
He performed acupuncture on her.

745
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,490
As a result,

746
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:27,660
two of her fingers can't move till now.

747
00:39:27,750 --> 00:39:28,690
Really?

748
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:31,400
Yes. Calling him here
is bringing harm to the kid.

749
00:39:31,720 --> 00:39:33,150
The doctor said I'm fine.

750
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,830
I will be all right in a couple of days.

751
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:36,310
How could it be all right?

752
00:39:36,410 --> 00:39:38,200
I'm telling you, if your
knee doesn't heal,

753
00:39:38,290 --> 00:39:39,960
it's going to hurt for
the rest of your life.

754
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:41,100
Exactly.

755
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:44,210
You are not going
to be limping, are you?

756
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,600
Don't jinx.

757
00:39:45,690 --> 00:39:46,670
Bah!

758
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:48,020
Bah!

759
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:49,710
Knee...

760
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,810
Be gentle.

761
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,040
Does it hurt?

762
00:39:52,130 --> 00:39:53,230
No, no.

763
00:39:53,710 --> 00:39:55,470
Let me know if you're in pain.

764
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:56,930
We must cure it in time.

765
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,250
Do you hear me?

766
00:39:58,350 --> 00:40:00,140
How about we buy some bones tomorrow

767
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:01,440
to make soup for her.

768
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:03,610
People benefit from what they eat, right?

769
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,690
Buy some bones.

770
00:40:05,870 --> 00:40:07,690
Okay, okay.

771
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,990
Stop talking, you two.

772
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:09,990
Leave us.

773
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:11,900
The patient needs rest.

774
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:13,190
Okay.

775
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:13,990
Let's go.

776
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:14,990
We are bothering them.

777
00:40:15,080 --> 00:40:16,310
Goodnight, Hua.

778
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,310
Goodnight.

779
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,380
Let me see.

780
00:40:22,130 --> 00:40:22,910
Do you feel any pain?

781
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,340
Let me give you a massage.

782
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:25,320
It hurts.

783
00:40:25,650 --> 00:40:26,990
Don't touch it.

784
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:28,380
Let me massage this leg for you.

785
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,970
Here, this leg.

786
00:40:35,310 --> 00:40:36,530
[Li Qing Tong.]

787
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,240
[If only you're always like this,]

788
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:40,860
[sweet and thoughtful.]

789
00:40:41,170 --> 00:40:44,090
[Who knew that you'd
grow up to be a man-eater?]

790
00:40:44,170 --> 00:40:45,980
[And curse with a straight face
every day.]

791
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,940
[If you remained like this,]

792
00:40:48,020 --> 00:40:50,180
[we wouldn't be quarrelling every day.]

793
00:40:52,010 --> 00:40:53,230
What's wrong?

794
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:55,060
Nothing.

795
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:57,010
I just think you are nice.

796
00:40:57,100 --> 00:40:58,030
Of course.

797
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,490
I think so too.

798
00:40:59,830 --> 00:41:01,340
So please don't scold me.

799
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:03,410
You are always scolding me.

800
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:08,370
Mum, I'm back.

801
00:41:08,460 --> 00:41:09,540
Wu Zhi Xun.

802
00:41:09,850 --> 00:41:10,980
Come here.

803
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:17,900
Where have you been?

804
00:41:18,550 --> 00:41:19,570
Library.

805
00:41:19,910 --> 00:41:21,130
Are you sure?
